rial temperatures.  Concentration-driven.", "relatedExperiments": [{"meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "type": "cim.2.designing.NumericalExperiment", "version": 1, "name": "ssp126", "id": "afd07a0e-b759-4ee8-abbd-f0bfd6ddd3dd"}, {"meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "type": "cim.2.designing.NumericalExperiment", "version": 1, "name": "ssp585-ext", "id": "15dc5a43-6c88-43f2-b379-b94a25ea361b"}, {"meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "type": "cim.2.designing.NumericalExperiment", "version": 1, "name": "ssp534-over-ext", "id": "0c5afce5-5a92-4c1f-83aa-b130e938464f"}], "relatedMips": [{"meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "type": "cim.2.designing.Project", "version": 1, "name": "ScenarioMIP", "id": "e02da263-c493-4ce0-a860-10ef9534ed7e"}], "internalName": "ScenarioMIP2.5", "canonicalName": "ssp126-ext", "citations": [{"meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "type": "cim.2.shared.Citation", "version": 1, "id": "6fa09901-c2c9-4584-b241-0328f8eea873"}, {"meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "type": "cim.2.shared.Citation", "version": 1, "id": "eeea1fe1-e498-4324-a718-9e499cb7ff2b"}, {"meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "type": "cim.2.shared.Citation", "version": 1, "id": "9e139643-3060-4b5b-9869-269f6d66c19b"}, {"meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "type": "cim.2.shared.Citation", "version": 1, "id": "a2b6129c-3a9d-4a49-8636-2f5be9a0c9c7"}], "meta": {"author": {"version": 1, "meta": {"type": "cim.2.shared.DocReference"}, "uid": "253825f3-fbc8-43fb-b1f6-cc575dc693eb"}, "createDate": "2016-07-04 13:00:00", "subProjects": ["ScenarioMIP"], "project": "cmip6-draft", "source": "spreadsheet", "version": 1, "updateDate": "2016-07-04 13:00:00", "type": "cim.2.designing.NumericalExperiment", "id": "0a0a292b-4b65-4b4c-8e7b-95d58c78f6a8"}, "rationale": "To investigate long term changes associated with a low forcing scenario. Inform analysis of the implications of the 1.5\u00b0C target. To allow investigation